  "page": "Temple of Memory",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Temple of Memory</b> is a temple in <a href=\"/index.php/Qarth\" title=\"Qarth\">Qarth</a> were petitioners seeking audience with the <a href=\"/index.php/Pureborn\" title=\"Pureborn\">Pureborn</a> must perform a traditional sacrifice, which is only the first of three steps to gain entry to the <a href=\"/index.php/Hall_of_a_Thousand_Thrones\" title=\"Hall of a Thousand Thrones\">Hall of a Thousand Thrones</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Temple_of_Memory&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_40\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 40\">Chapter 40</a>, Daenerys III.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260405003700\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.009 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.010 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 130/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8534/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 424/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 22/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40